abstract: Bill Pennington On Football column says New York Giants quarterback Eli Manning provided most of the offense in team's 20-17 win over Miami Dolphins.
snippet: Quarterback Eli Manning provided most of the offense Sunday in the Giants’ 20-17 win over the Dolphins, throwing for 2 touchdowns and 19 of his team’s 21 first downs.
lead_paragraph: Quarterback Eli Manning provided most of the offense Sunday in the Giants’ 20-17 win over the Dolphins, throwing for 2 touchdowns and 19 of his team’s 21 first downs.

headline.main: A Steady Arm Lifts a Shaky Team
headline.print_headline: A Steady Arm Lifts a Shaky Team
headline.seo: Manning Steadies Shaky Giants in Win Over Dolphins
